('George Harrison', 'George Harrison MBE was an English guitarist, singer-songwriter, and producer who achieved international fame as the lead guitarist of the Beatles.', 'images/harrison.jpg'),
('Rakky Curvelo', 'My name is Raquelline Curvelo and I start to believe that someday I would be a web developer when I was studing in my high school. I mean, I always like computer, so, why not?\r\n\r\nYears after that, I started to study a bachelors degree in Information Systems and that\'s where I face boolean numbers and variables for the first time. I gave up and started another bachelous in journalism, but I was always with that in mind...\r\n\r\nNow, as a student of Applied Digital Media, one of my activities at Griffith College was create a website with a films database, proving that I know how to deal with HMTL, CSS, PHP and MySQL. Let\'s see what I got!', 'images/me_.jpg'),
('Ringo Starr', 'Sir Richard Starkey MBE, known professionally as Ringo Starr, is an English musician, songwriter, singer, and actor who gained worldwide fame as the drummer for the Beatles.', 'images/starr.png');

